{"tid":2030302,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"寫左首歌, 送比成日訓唔著既你","createTime":"2020-05-22T16:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T00:55:23.000Z","uid":328767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"957ac285af181e7b02d1d7e3e2661cfa9221acab","tid":2030302,"uid":328767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:09:14.000Z","msg":"呢首歌係有一排我自己好大壓力果陣寫出黎既, <br />\n講真自從上年, 想有一晚訓翻個好教都得來不易...所以先寫左呢首歌 - 'Sweet Dream'.<br />\n本來我都好少做呢種類型既歌, 今次真係本住希望用音樂幫下人減壓, relax下訓個好教呢個諗法而寫出黎, 不過好在成品都唔差, 相信都真係有healing既作用既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n送比大家, 'Sweet Dream'. 希望聽到呢首歌既你可以暫時放低所有煩惱, 發翻個好夢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oyy3FYRq8RU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOyy3FYRq8RU&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=344f3c81\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oyy3FYRq8RU</a><br />\n鍾意既話麻煩CLS, 希望可以令更多香港人聽到呢首歌啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算只係幾分鐘都好, 希望呢首歌幫到你relax啦~Thanks"},{"pid":"b677cca46667a8dd81d16f1cb2addc5f12bb949b","tid":2030302,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"幾好呀 開頭拍子細聲d就好"},{"pid":"9394852f30d10b8dcff4b2cecc5561d144e17b1b","tid":2030302,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"多謝<br />\n你一定溝死女"},{"pid":"77faa336c0661d7ba22f3f46df17fe08eca59fc5","tid":2030302,"uid":328767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9394852f30d10b8dcff4b2cecc5561d144e17b1b","tid":2030302,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:09:51.000Z","msg":"多謝<br />\n你一定溝死女"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:39:14.000Z","msg":"前提係要有女比我溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78c4b5d42dcfeff5d8224ae300b9c32